          		<div class="col-md-9 ftco-animate pb-5 text-center">
          			<p class="breadcrumbs"><span class="mr-2"><a href="../">Home <i class="ion-ios-arrow-forward"></i></a></span> <span>Laptop List <i class="ion-ios-arrow-forward"></i></span></p>
